snippet.title: TURNING AMBER HEARD INTO MERA FROM THE DC UNIVERSE! *SPEED-ART*
snippet.description:
Hi all! I haven't done an artwork for Amber Heard and her character 'Mera' in a while, and so I decided to recreate/revamp an old piece I did when I first started. Hope you like it :D

Enjoy!

Make sure to Like and Subscribe if you enjoyed the video! and feel free to comment down below your thoughts on the video!
Join the Notification Squad by Clicking the Bell to be notified when I post!
